Swiss Close Emissions Trading Registry After Security Review

-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 
2011-02-17T15:17:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/swiss-authorities-close-emissions-trading-registry-after-security-review.html
The Swiss emissions trading registry
has been closed after routine security checks this week revealed
“the system is vulnerable to attack,” the federal office for
information technology said today in an e-mailed statement. The
Swiss FOEN office for the environment and the information
technology agency are working to reinforce security, the
statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in Zurich at 
